es/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"065c1ac3302334eda1afe192c3e2e99db1c86dcd","tid":256843,"uid":4308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:02:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.goal.com/hk/news/505/%E6%AD%90%E9%9C%B8%E7%9B%83/2015/08/27/14807372/%E6%91%A9%E9%80%A3%E5%A5%B4%E6%AD%90%E9%9C%B8%E7%9B%83%E5%86%A0%E8%BB%8D%E6%AF%AB%E7%84%A1%E6%84%8F%E7%BE%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.goal.com%2Fhk%2Fnews%2F505%2F%25E6%25AD%2590%25E9%259C%25B8%25E7%259B%2583%2F2015%2F08%2F27%2F14807372%2F%25E6%2591%25A9%25E9%2580%25A3%25E5%25A5%25B4%25E6%25AD%2590%25E9%259C%25B8%25E7%259B%2583%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%25BB%258D%25E6%25AF%25AB%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%2584%258F%25E7%25BE%25A9&d=wXXh3%2FvEyoclwUBZuqJaJJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=dc798137\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.goal.com/hk/news/505/%E6%AD%90%E9%9C%B8%E7%9B%83/2015/08/27/14807372/%E6%91%A9%E9%80%A3%E5%A5%B4%E6%AD%90%E9%9C%B8%E7%9B%83%E5%86%A0%E8%BB%8D%E6%AF%AB%E7%84%A1%E6%84%8F%E7%BE%A9</a><br />\n<br />\n摩連奴認為歐霸盃賽事對於大球會來說毫無意義&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n車路士領隊摩連奴表示，對於「藍戰士」這種級別的球隊來說，贏下歐霸盃冠軍根本算不上是一件好事。<br />\n<br />\n賓尼迪斯在2012-13球季曾率領車路士取得了球會歷史上首座的歐霸盃冠軍，不過摩帥卻認為這個獎盃毫無意義。<br />\n<br />\n在BT Sport製作的一部摩連奴的紀錄片中，該名葡萄牙教頭如此說：「當我回到車路士的時候，我感覺到球隊參加歐霸盃的經歷是毫無益處的。」<br />\n<br />\n「歐霸盃根本沒辦法和歐聯相比。無論是這項賽事的水準、參賽的球員、球隊和歐聯都不是一個等級的。一家大球會參加和贏得歐霸盃冠軍是毫無益處的一件事。」"},{"pid":"a062334aef588496d89c5f89ae92dbca3199c4aa","tid":256843,"uid":97115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:04:23.000Z","msg":"好酸"},{"pid":"4f7480cfd37ee23342acb721619f537c3758d914","tid":256843,"uid":283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:36:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.goal.com/hk/news/505/%E6%AD%90%E9%9C%B8%E7%9B%83/2015/08/27/14807372/%E6%91%A9%E9%80%A3%E5%A5%B4%E6%AD%90%E9%9C%B8%E7%9B%83%E5%86%A0%E8%BB%8D%E6%AF%AB%E7%84%A1%E6%84%8F%E7%BE%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.